WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.967 --> 00:00:04.303
SO UH YOUR OFFICE IS ALL THE WAY
DOWN AT THE END.

00:00:04.336 --> 00:00:05.404
- MM-HMM.

00:00:05.437 --> 00:00:06.939
- YOU HAVE YOUR OWN ATTACHED
BATHROOM, BY THE WAY.

00:00:06.972 --> 00:00:08.975
OH, UM, HERE'S ONE
OF OUR BEST RESEARCHERS.

00:00:09.008 --> 00:00:10.476
DICK?
- HEY.

00:00:10.509 --> 00:00:12.378
- AH, HELLO THERE.

00:00:12.411 --> 00:00:15.114
[dramatic music]
WHAT'S UP, DUDE?

00:00:15.147 --> 00:00:17.350
GLAD TO SEE
THERE'S ANOTHER BROTHER

00:00:17.383 --> 00:00:19.452
IN THIS STUFFY PLACE.

00:00:19.485 --> 00:00:23.222
- SO, UH, THIS IS GONNA BE
YOUR ASSISTANT, GENEVIEVE.

00:00:23.255 --> 00:00:24.891
[dramatic music]
- WHAT IS THIS?

00:00:24.924 --> 00:00:26.859
- IT'S THE SHINING, MAN.

00:00:26.892 --> 00:00:28.928
ALL BLACK PEOPLE
HAVE THE SHINING.

00:00:28.961 --> 00:00:30.863
YOU NEVER SHINED WITH
ANOTHER BLACK PERSON BEFORE?

00:00:30.896 --> 00:00:32.932
- NO, I GREW UP

00:00:32.965 --> 00:00:34.734
IN A WHITE NEIGHBORHOOD
AND THEN WENT TO DARTMOUTH.

00:00:34.767 --> 00:00:35.902
I'VE MET
OTHER BLACK PEOPLE BEFORE,

00:00:35.935 --> 00:00:38.037
BUT NOT LIKE THIS.

00:00:38.070 --> 00:00:40.373
- YOU GOTTA GET SHINED AT
BY ANOTHER BLACK PERSON FIRST,

00:00:40.406 --> 00:00:42.575
AND THEN YOU GET IT.
IT'S KINDA LIKE FACEBOOK.

00:00:45.377 --> 00:00:48.614
[dramatic music]
- WHAT UP, DUDES?

00:00:48.647 --> 00:00:50.049
- SO EVERY BLACK PERSON
HAS THIS?

00:00:50.082 --> 00:00:51.884
IS KOBE LISTENING?

00:00:51.917 --> 00:00:53.186
- [voice of Kobe Bryant]
YO, WHAT UP?

00:00:53.219 --> 00:00:55.221
- WOW! DENZEL WASHINGTON?

00:00:55.254 --> 00:00:56.923
- [voice of Denzel Washington]
I'M HERE, I'M PRESENT,

00:00:56.956 --> 00:00:57.957
AND I WILL ALWAYS
BE AROUND.

00:00:57.990 --> 00:00:59.625
- LIL JON?

00:00:59.658 --> 00:01:01.627
- [voice of Lil Jon]
YEAH!

00:01:01.660 --> 00:01:02.728
- [voice of Barack Obama]
EXCUSE ME, LIL JON.

00:01:02.761 --> 00:01:04.464
WELCOME, RAY.

00:01:04.497 --> 00:01:06.299
I'M GLAD TO HAVE YOU
ON BOARD.

00:01:06.332 --> 00:01:08.568
- OH, [bleep]!
WHAT'S UP, BARACK OBAMA?

00:01:10.569 --> 00:01:12.338
AHEM!

00:01:12.371 --> 00:01:14.507
[chuckles]

00:01:14.540 --> 00:01:16.376
WOULDN'T THAT BE SOMETHING
IF BARACK OBAMA JUST SHOWED UP?

00:01:18.377 --> 00:01:21.314
- YOUR START-UP PAPERWORK'S
RIGHT OVER HERE.

00:01:21.347 --> 00:01:22.849
[dramatic music]
- MAN, YOU GOTTA BE

00:01:22.882 --> 00:01:24.350
MORE CAREFUL.

00:01:24.383 --> 00:01:26.152
LEARN TO USE THE SHINING.

00:01:26.185 --> 00:01:28.154
TUNE IN AND OUT OF IT.
OTHERWISE,

00:01:28.187 --> 00:01:30.523
YOU WON'T BE ABLE
TO SORT OUT WHO'S TALKING.

00:01:30.556 --> 00:01:32.191
- AND I'M SICK OF THESE
GODDAMN SNAKES...

00:01:32.224 --> 00:01:33.459
- JUST GIVE ME
THE BASKETBALL!

00:01:33.492 --> 00:01:35.428
- ON THIS GODDAMN PLANE!

00:01:35.461 --> 00:01:37.330
- HERE, YO, COCO, WHAT
YOU WANT TO DRINK, GIRL?

00:01:37.363 --> 00:01:39.098
- LEO, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:01:39.131 --> 00:01:41.000
- DRINK SOME COLT 45
MALT LIQUOR.

00:01:41.033 --> 00:01:43.102
[overlapping voices]
- WOMEN DIG CHOCOLATE!

00:01:43.135 --> 00:01:45.138
- IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

00:01:45.171 --> 00:01:47.373
[dramatic music]
- RAY!

00:01:47.406 --> 00:01:49.842
LISTEN FOR MORGAN.
MORGAN FREEMAN.

00:01:49.875 --> 00:01:51.944
HE WILL GUIDE YOU.

00:01:51.977 --> 00:01:54.147
- [voice of Morgan Freeman]
LISTEN TO MY VOICE, RAY.

00:01:54.180 --> 00:01:58.284
NOW, JUST STAY CALM
AND FOCUS ON THAT WHITE MAN.

00:01:58.317 --> 00:02:00.386
- [exhales]

00:02:00.419 --> 00:02:02.555
EVERYTHING'S
GOING TO BE OKAY.

00:02:02.588 --> 00:02:04.357
- ONCE YOU FINISH UP
THIS PAPERWORK,

00:02:04.390 --> 00:02:05.925
BRING IT TO JENNIFER
IN MY OFFICE.

00:02:08.627 --> 00:02:11.330
- [voice of Morgan Freeman]
NOW, PICK UP THAT LETTER OPENER,

00:02:11.363 --> 00:02:14.534
AND KILL THAT WHITE MAN.

